502:     *   Add a `TextField("Testosterone Level", text: $valueText)`. Use `.keyboardType(.decimalPad)`.
503:     *   Add a `Picker("Unit", selection: $selectedUnit)` with `Text("ng/dL").tag("ng/dL")` and `Text("nmol/L").tag("nmol/L")`.
